e&quot;:&quot;2023 年耳机世界一切如常，但是明年应该会带来一些改变 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23999795/earbuds-headphones-2024-preview-apple-samsung-sonos&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bose QuietComfort Earbuds II 评测：降噪统治 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23353777/bose-quietcomfort-earbuds-2-review&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;rxqLbH&quot;>;Bose 粉丝很难接受 299 美元的 QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞升级版，它毫不客气地将 QuietComfort Earbuds II 从地位上踢了下来，成为该公司的招牌耳塞...... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24065902/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-earbuds-dji-mini-2-se-drone-avatar-游戏销售-交易&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24065902/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-earbuds-dji-mini-2-se-drone-avatar-game-sale-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24065902/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-earbuds-dji-mini-2-se-drone-avatar-game-sale-deal</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-08T13:00:03-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-08T13:00:03-05:00</updated><title> FCC 禁止使用人工智能生成的语音进行机器人呼叫</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两部智能手机放在黄色背景上的插图，上面有红色胶带，上面写着“危险”&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/viHUOgU6hExU71YusSJMn83HKzw=/0x0: 2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73122871/akrales_220309_4977_0336.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id =&quot;I1mbz6&quot;>;美国联邦通信委员会规定自动电话使用人工智能生成的语音为非法行为。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.fcc.gov/public/attachments/DOC-400393A1.pdf&quot;>;周四发布的裁决&lt;/a>;赋予州总检察长对使用人工智能的来电者采取行动的能力语音克隆技术。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;X8DTos&quot;>;正如&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.fcc.gov/public/attachments/FCC-24-17A1.pdf&quot;>;裁决中概述的&lt; /a>;，根据《电话消费者保护法》(TCPA)，人工智能生成的语音现在被视为“人工或预先录制的语音”。这限制了呼叫者出于非紧急目的或未经事先同意而使用人工智能生成的语音。 TCPA 禁止各种自动呼叫做法，包括使用“人造或预先录制的语音”来传递消息，但没有明确说明这是否包括人工智能驱动的语音克隆。新裁决澄清...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24066169/fcc-robocall-ai-voices-ban&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24066169/fcc-robocall-ai-voices-ban" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/8/24066169/fcc-robocall-ai-voices-ban</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>